text: Icimauna angaba is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Martins and Galileo in 1991. It is known from Costa Rica.BioLib.cz - Icimauna angaba. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1991
title: Icimauna angaba
